14. Safety and approval workflow
15. Development roadmap
16. Suggested folder structure
17. Recommended first GitHub repository structure
18. Example data models
19. Example API endpoints
20. Example UI screens

Focus on creating a realistic plan that can be built incrementally, starting with NC parsing and setup sheet generation before expanding into full tooling and fixture inventory.
